      "text": "Download the package, either xforms-techniques.tar.gz , or xforms-techniques.zip (for Windows), and unpack it somewhere Run the (tiny) server: in the top-level folder, there is a program called \"xcontents\", versions for Linux, Windows, Mac, and Raspberry Pi.",
